==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Relevancy
<hw>Rel"e*van*cy</hw> <pr>(-v<it>a</it>n*s?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>n.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>The quality or state of being relevant; pertinency;
applicability.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Its answer little meaning, little <qex>relevancy</qex> bore.</q>
<rj><qau>Poe.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Scots Law)</fld> <def>Sufficiency to infer the
conclusion.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Relevant</ent>⟦br⟧
